Clinical effectiveness and cost-effectiveness of imatinib dose escalation for 
the treatment of unresectable and/or metastatic gastrointestinal stromal tumours 
that have progressed on treatment at a dose of 400 mg/day: a systematic review 
and economic evaluation.

Hislop J(1), Quayyum Z, Elders A, Fraser C, Jenkinson D, Mowatt G, Sharma P, 
